Privacy Policy for  Spendwise

At Spendwise, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our app.

1. Information We Collect

Location Information: Our app requests permission to access your device's location to track your hikes. This information is only used to provide location-based features such as mapping and tracking your hikes.
Account Information: To use the app, you will need to create an account. The information we collect during registration may include your name, email address, and a password.
Hike Data: Your hike details, such as route, distance, and time, are collected when you track a hike using the app.
2. Use of Information

We use the information we collect to:

Provide and improve the app's location-based services.
Allow you to log in and manage your account.
Enable you to track your hikes and share your progress with others.
Display hikes from other users if you have set your profile to public.
3. Sharing Your Hike Data

Public Hikes: If you set your profile to "public," other users will be able to see your hikes. You have the ability to change this setting at any time to make your hikes private.
Location Data: We do not share your exact location with other users unless it is part of the public hikes you choose to share.
4. Data Security

We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmitting data over the internet or storing data is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee the security of your information.

5. Third-Party Services

Our app may use third-party services, such as analytics tools, to help us understand how users interact with the app. These third parties may have access to your information but are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose.

6. Your Rights

You have the right to:

Access the information we hold about you.
Correct or update your account information.
Delete your account at any time by contacting us.
Change your privacy settings, including making your hikes private.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the updated policy within the app. Your continued use of the app after the changes are made constitutes your acceptance of the revised privacy policy.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at co-3d@hotmail.com.
